    "body": "\r\nProblem:\r\nBuild fails if user cloned the repo to a path with \"%\" chars:\r\n\r\n    src/gen/gen_char_blob.lua:51: bad argument #1 to 'format' (number expected, got string)\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\n- Escape \"%\" chars.\r\n- Also use \"%q\" in case the path has spaces...\r\n\r\nfix #39271",
